title: Appendix A - MediationZone Interfaces - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: MediationZone provides connection interfaces to a variety of external systems. Interfaces are grouped into two categories: Offline interfaces Collection and forwarding interfaces specifically used in a file-based environment. Online Interfaces Client and server functionality for workflows that communicate over online-enabled interfaces. For more detailed information: Refer to Product Catalog
